{"tid":1420420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗記者會，可唔可以整個新聞報導","createTime":"2019-08-06T04:32:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T04:36:24.000Z","uid":42164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"24d16e994b6e9c25e226fc9404f64fda379fb7a3","tid":1420420,"uid":42164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:32:23.000Z","msg":"有文宣巴打話呢排每日都太多資訊，有少少唔知煲邊單好<br />\n的確，最近戰線比較多，資訊好分散<br />\n有冇辦法可以整個新聞報導，類似以前毛記/而家喱show個啲咁？<br />\n可以報導同記錄每日警察濫權、黑社會暴行<br />\n受眾對於視像文宣亦會睇得投入啲<br />\n然後喺每則報導後面我哋加返定性，例如本台譴責XXX之類<br />\n喺新聞完結前又可以預告嚟緊既活動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">既然我哋可以搞記者會抗衡政府<br />\n唔知又可唔可以搞個新聞報導對抗無綫呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">希望推到有media/ youtuber幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"e93fbeb15de1feefe2784b6c504123e4726d6847","tid":1420420,"uid":42164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:33:27.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8fcbd57c254159cc6e9dfe23515c8e276ae6928","tid":1420420,"uid":215505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:33:28.000Z","msg":"搵大j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0df94ba171a751a2ee7287c12417852d27ee66","tid":1420420,"uid":42164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8fcbd57c254159cc6e9dfe23515c8e276ae6928","tid":1420420,"uid":215505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:33:28.000Z","msg":"搵大j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:33:48.000Z","msg":"如果佢肯幫手就好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d6e7ad3bf058f38cd4eae027acbbbbf5e2ab0a","tid":1420420,"uid":42164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:36:24.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}